message.entry: With {0,number,integer} bin edges, you must specify {1,number,integer} category names.
Specify either unique data values or bin edges, but not both.
Input data must be a real numeric array when you specify bin edges.
Bin edges must be a real numeric vector with at least two elements.
Unable to create unique category names from the bin edges using 5 significant digits. Specify category names using the CATEGORYNAMES input argument.
